Company Name: Filing and Packing Materials Manufacturing Co (2180)
Description: Filing and Packing Materials Manufacturing Co (known as: Fipco) is a public company, listed on Saudi Stock Exchange “Tadawul” (TDWL) since June 1991. Fipco operates within the Materials sector focusing on Paper Packaging. Fipco is based in Riyadh, Saudi Arabia and was established in June 1991.
